{"tid":1244731,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有人屌民陣623星期日唔搞遊行，大家真係覺得如果照搞係好事？","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T05:47:57.000Z","uid":257422,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb46f3c0bacf5508d64c79b33ff40755eb7e790","tid":1244731,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"69 一百萬零三人出黎，相信好多都係真心出黎，唔係為打卡而係為表態。<br />\n<br />\n但616 有2m人出黎，其實好多都係受到612 既警察暴力而出，我身邊都好多政治冷感既係見69 多人出，見有得打卡先出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(拿我唔係要批鬥打卡，因為起碼佢地出左黎表態)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我好肯定</span>, 好多人已經因為暫緩、道歉而放低左件事、好多人因為已經打左一次卡就覺得任務完成、好多人因為69、612、616出左黎而覺得攰，未必會再可以行多一次6,7 個鐘既遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果今個星期再搞，我當你都仲有一百萬人出黎(但我都唔覺得會有) ，咁咪有哂原因俾政府/建制 話市民既不滿已經慢慢化解、已經對政府既有返信心？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我唔認為623 唔搞係一個錯既決定<br />\n我地應該繼續著手搞不合作運動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亦唔該民陣 全力支持 621 同埋搞好你個 71 遊行！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cbaff3bfd13a49e86684033ea05c61ca4b1dd4","tid":1244731,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"大家點睇？"},{"pid":"1478bbdb001466a2d79b9b19dba1a103a885039e","tid":1244731,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid